{"tid":106110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(雙非)川普下一步遏止生育旅遊？《北京遇上西雅圖》恐成絕響","createTime":"2017-02-03T11:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T13:35:25.000Z","uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a0c9858b8d465609785cc8aacaba418b022c0b","tid":106110,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"川普下一步遏止生育旅遊？《北京遇上西雅圖》恐成絕響<br />\n<br />\n2017/02/03 12:25&nbsp;7371<br />\n<br />\n繼簽署限制難民、興建美墨長城的行政命令後，美國總統川普要向境內居留的外國人開刀？中國內部的社群媒體廣傳，川普的幕僚已經草擬另一項行政命令，研議遏止「生育旅遊」（Birth Tourism）。類似電影《北京遇上西雅圖》的劇情，可能將成為絕響。<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》報導，在新浪微博廣傳名為「限制社會福利」的草案，旨在確保移民家庭不會使用美國的社會福利，其中包括將研議反制「生育旅遊」的項目。<br />\n<br />\n此命令若通過，代表行政部門將會統計移民家庭5年內，使用美國社會福利包括現金補助、醫療補助（Medicaid）、兒童健康計畫、食物券等福利的使用狀態，並要求國土安全部遣返這些使用福利的移民。此外，擔保這些新移民的單位或個人，需償還政府撥出的福利金額。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，遏制生育旅遊的家庭，可以有效防止非法移民父母，為了取得社會保障而刻意在美國產下美國公民。<br />\n（北美中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170203/1048117/papersec_right\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170203%2F1048117%2Fpapersec_right&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhphv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f2eec95b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170203/1048117/papersec_right</a>"},{"pid":"8800a5ed6b56144513899aa3eb87b6d597efaff1","tid":106110,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲無法產卵"},{"pid":"0dd453922478e1c8b7229f7c6ae88c87fadaa694","tid":106110,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46d64ba93ed5b1f60f77ac0f5da139c2afc0605","tid":106110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c452ac7e331cabcbb0b34214ecf39242125f4e","tid":106110,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"香港呢次仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667d83c140de451cfbe6032215193f154bf7c33a","tid":106110,"uid":49678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"加拿大之前講過咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b97d8d5fa32c63528f7e308edb723691baabd96","tid":106110,"uid":53677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96ee229d36873628f022fbd912e045661cf7456","tid":106110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fada58bef33be03d944cc671706e9b9d7e80d79","tid":106110,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加拿大之前講過咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加拿大好似block左"},{"pid":"00364a8397199c1047bdee0e7f00728b07ea24ab","tid":106110,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加拿大之前講過咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加拿大好似block左</blockquote><br />\nsource?"}]}